<p>A South Korean special prosecutor has indicted former president Yoon Suk Yeol, accusing him of ordering drone flights over North Korea to create a pretext for declaring martial law last December, prosecutors said on Monday. The new charges include allegations of aiding the enemy and other national security violations; prosecutors say the plan was part of a bid to stoke tensions that would justify emergency rule. The indictment adds to an ongoing legal crisis: Yoon was removed from office earlier this year and remains the subject of multiple probes and a separate insurrection trial.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/HPBnKSmXHA75Y80bUe9tOB50niD_AloT7QuwWQMQ258_FN9xUCMM0_i6VkJRUNc2ExtfS3ND7lLb67wBliOoCL-VnJ_lvjxH8Ki8LDF1RqMqiBaO76_VNVVUYPy161lNztS9F_CikSu_6wqXmlz7FzWGpS3fg8zFZ_ouKCJ25TYMbdFdstRvfPaZ_PcosiNu8z0NKE8hZa5dPsbE' alt='Yoon Suk Yeol, former president of South Korea, arriving at his trial in Seoul in April; prosecutors say he ordered drone flights to justify martial law [nytimes.com#1].' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Specific charges: Prosecutors charged Yoon with aiding the enemy and national security violations tied to the alleged drone flights and related actions.</li><li>Parliament confrontation: Investigators say Yoon dispatched armed soldiers to the National Assembly to try to stop lawmakers from blocking his martial law declaration in December 2024.</li><li>Special investigation: A special probe opened earlier this year focused on whether Yoon ordered the drone operations, producing evidence that led to Monday&#x27;s indictment.</li><li>Courtroom presence: Yoon has already appeared in court this year during hearings related to his brief martial law declaration and his broader legal troubles.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Special prosecutor&#x27;s office: Prosecutors say Yoon ordered drone flights into North Korea to create a pretext for declaring martial law and to provoke a military incident that would justify emergency powers. (<a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/south-korea-special-prosecutor-indicts-ex-president-yoon-on-more-charges/article70261400.ece'>The Hindu</a>)</li><li>Yoon&#x27;s defense / allies: Yoon&#x27;s camp has denied wrongdoing and framed the investigations as politically charged, while contesting prosecutors&#x27; characterizations of his actions. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/south-korea-s-ex-president-yoon-indicted-on-new-charges/a-74681478'>DW</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/south-korea-special-prosecutor-indicts-ex-president-yoon-on-more-charges/article70261400.ece'>South Koreaâ€™s ousted leader Yoon indicted for flying drones over North Korea</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/11/10/world/asia/drones-korea-martial-law-yoon.html'>Drones Over North Korea Were Part of Martial Law Bid in South, Special Counsel Says</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2025/11/10/south-korea-indicts-ex-president-yoon-for-aiding-enemy_6747299_4.html'>South Korea indicts ex-president Yoon for aiding enemy</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/south-korea-s-ex-president-yoon-indicted-on-new-charges/a-74681478'>South Korea&#x27;s ex-president Yoon indicted on new charges</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/south-koreas-ousted-leader-yoon-indicted-flying-drones-127367354'>South Korea&#x27;s ousted leader Yoon indicted for flying drones over North Korea</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/south-korean-prosecutor-charges-former-president-yoon-over-national-security-violations-13949322.html'>South Korean prosecutor charges former president Yoon over national security violations</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/10/south-korea-indicts-ex-leader-yoon-on-charges-of-aiding-the-enemy'>South Korea indicts ex-leader Y